DESCRIPTION:Thursday June 4 – Aug 69:30 – 10:30 am11:00 am – 12:00 pm \n\n\
	n\n$10 member / $12 nonmember (per child\, per class)Ages 2-4 \n\n\n\nEach
	 child must be accompanied by their guardian. Siblings are welcome to atte
	nd but must be registered to participate. \n\n\n\nFamily Tree Membership a
	nd above required for member discount. \n\n\n\nOur youngest naturalists ar
	e invited to join us for hands-on nature exploration. This program is a pe
	rfect way for our Little Explorers to discover more about the natural worl
	d around them.  \n\n\n\nPlease come dressed for the outdoors\, including c
